> It&#x27;s either more difficult to implement this<p>Something like this should be enough<p><pre><code>    &quot;topiconesubtopictwo&quot; [label = &quot;subtopic two&quot;];
    &quot;topictwosubtopictwo&quot; [label = &quot;subtopic two&quot;];
</code></pre>
Or alternatively you can use a counter.<p><pre><code>    12 [label = &#x27;subtopic two&#x27;];
    22 [label = &#x27;subtopic two&#x27;];
</code></pre>
If you avoid spaces you can also forget the quotes (but quotes are safer)<p><pre><code>     topiconesubtopictwo [label = &quot;subtopic two&quot;];
</code></pre>
But avoid to name nodes with &#x27;_&#x27; and &#x27;.&#x27;<p><pre><code>     topic_one_subtopic_two [label, etc...]
     topic.one.subtopic.two [label, etc...]</code></pre>
